highlights.text: “Dream Come True” by Freya Skye, Malachi Barton, ZOMBIES – Cast, and Disney is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Norway, up 28 spots at #60.
“The Glen - Levi Heron Edit” by Levi Heron has been on Viral Songs Norway the longest, at 84 days straight.
Vestavind has the most spots on Viral Songs Norway. “Ligga” is the highest at #1.
“Arab dak - Extended Version” by Diekel is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Norway at #53.
